{"id":286078,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/香港獨立媒體-here器材篇：街拍的器材what-do-i-need-for-street-photography/","date":"2013-03-26T10:30:53Z","modified":"2013-03-26T10:30:53Z","title":"香港獨立媒體 | here器材篇：街拍的器材(What do I need for street photography?)","content":"<p><p> </p>\n<p> <br />\n<strong>不適合的器材(Camera not street photography)</strong><br />\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD85813.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10603\" alt=\"_KSD8581\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD85813-266x400.jpg\" width=\"266\" height=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p>街頭拍攝意思是在街頭拍攝真實的環境，但是當你拎著這樣大的相機再加那麼搶眼的相機帶，這裡會令到街上的人都會害怕你。ZOOM鏡對我來說，十分重，光圈細，我會選擇定焦鏡及大光圈的鏡。</p>\n<p>Street photography is all about what is happening on the street , no taking about you have a expensive camera or lens . I will not use the big camera like D3s and a zoom lens for street photography. That is too heavy , people will stay away from you .<br />\n<strong>較為適合的器材(Camera for street photography)</strong><br />\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/DSC_02141.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10604\" alt=\"DSC_0214\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/DSC_02141-600x400.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p>這是我常用的裝備，一細部小的D700，加上50mm 1.8D  （影相不是講鏡頭的，所以用枝平價鏡就可以了：））當然，要把那麼搶眼的相機帶拆走。</p>\n<p>I using my small D700 and a 50mm 1.8D (cheap lens can also get some great pictures)</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>用1.8D拍的</p>\n<p>Pictures from 1.8D</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD6553.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10621\" alt=\"_KSD6553\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD6553-600x400.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></a><br />\n<strong>菲林機(Film camera)</strong><br />\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD8582.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10592\" alt=\"_KSD8582\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD8582-600x400.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p>我覺得最方便的都是LOMO的LC﹣WIDE，不用對焦，細部，加上17MM的鏡頭，不用看觀景器也可以拍照</p>\n<p>I also use Lomo&#8217;s LC-wide , no need to focus , it is very small . I can take pictures without looking her viewfinder (cause she has 17mm lens)</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>以下的相是來自LC﹣WIDE</p>\n<p>photos from LC-wide</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img4701.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10616\" alt=\"img470\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img4701-600x374.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"374\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img4741.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10617\" alt=\"img474\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img4741-600x374.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"374\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img475.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10618\" alt=\"img475\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img475-600x374.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"374\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img4792.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10619\" alt=\"img479\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img4792-600x357.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"357\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD85863.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10605\" alt=\"_KSD8586\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/KSD85863-600x400.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p>有時我會帶F3，因為相對較結實，當年最高級的相機，可以不用怕會撞壞喔</p>\n<p>A Nice standard camera !!</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Photo from F3</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img2281.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-10622\" alt=\"img228\" src=\"http://90sfoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/img2281-245x400.jpg\" width=\"245\" height=\"400\" /></a></p>\n<p> <code>我們並不善於用文字表達自已，我們相信用相或許更能表達自已<br />\n其他作品：<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://90sfoto.com\" title=\"Website\">Website</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/90sfoto\" title=\"Facebook\">Facebook</a></code></p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,8712,14403]}